headline: 1 Wall Street Analyst Thinks Lowe's Stock Is Going to $310. Is It a Buy?
summary: Following its third-quarter earnings report, a slew of Wall Street analysts recently raised their price targets on Lowe's Companies (NYSE: LOW).  Truist's Scot Ciccarelli raised his target to $310 while maintaining a buy rating on the stock.  Wall Street has warmed to the home improvement sector this year, hoping to profit from a falling-interest-rate environment.
